From au cleveland Freenet Edu Dr Joshua Backon Subject Re West Bank and Baseball In September , our medical reserve unit was sent to the KETZIOT prison camp to take care of Arab prisoner who were housed in sections of prisoners each, with each section subdivided in units housing prisoners The prisoners would communicate with other distant sections sometimes yards away by taking stones, tying written notes to the stones, and throwing them with incredible precision to other sections I should have been a recruiter for the Red Sox There were at least three prisoners who could have been outstanding pitchers Josh backon VMS HUJI AC IL